---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - PB Dodgeball">
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-4">About Us</h1>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[rgb(248,187,4)] mx-auto"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Club Values Section -->
    <section class="mb-20">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Club Values</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/80 mb-4">
          At PB, our number one objective is to ensure <em class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">everyone</em> is having
          a good time, whether they're coming along for the first time, or they're
          playing at our highest levels of competition. To reinforce this, we have
          established some clear values that all players and members are required
          to adhere by.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/80">
          These values go beyond the behaviour expected within our sessions, and
          apply to our innate values as people, if you find that you align with
          these values, then PB is the place for you!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <article class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[rgb(248,187,4)]/30 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[rgb(248,187,4)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#0b0b10]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-3">Respect</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80">Showing respect for opponents, officials, and teammates alike.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[rgb(248,187,4)]/30 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[rgb(248,187,4)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#0b0b10]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-3">Inclusivity</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80">Welcoming and valuing diversity among players.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[rgb(248,187,4)]/30 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[rgb(248,187,4)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#0b0b10]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-3">Humility</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80">Remaining humble and respectful in victory, and gracious in defeat.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-6 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-[rgb(248,187,4)]/30 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[rgb(248,187,4)] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#0b0b10]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-3">Integrity</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80">
            Conducting ourselves with honesty and ethical behaviour both on and
            off the court.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-white mb-12">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <article class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-8 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[rgb(248,187,4)]/30 transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-4">Who are we?</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
            PB Dodgeball is a local Bromley community club, we're a non-profit so
            any money raised by the club goes straight back into the club to fund
            hall hire, equipment, competition entry fees etc.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-8 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[rgb(248,187,4)]/30 transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-4">Why do we exist?</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
            We exist to share our love of dodgeball with the local community,
            getting people together to socialize, exercise and to make friends.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-8 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[rgb(248,187,4)]/30 transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-4">Who can play?</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
            PB Dodgeball is open to <em class="text-yellow-500 font-semibold">anyone</em> aged 16 and over, we play mixed
            gender sessions with a variety of age ranges and abilities
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-8 hover:shadow-md hover:border-[rgb(248,187,4)]/30 transition-all">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-4">Is it competitive?</h3>
          <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Our weekly sessions are "Social dodgeball" where the aim of the
            session is primarily to socialize and have fun, we play different
            variations of dodgeball for a more casual session.
          </p>
          <p class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
            For the more competitive members, we offer signups for tournaments,
            leagues and inter-club matches.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
